# 🚀 Day 65/90 – Build the Upload Progress Screen

Welcome to **Day 65!**

Today we'll make the upload process feel like a real application.

Currently, when the user taps **CONTINUE**, they only see a SnackBar.

Today we'll change the flow to:

```text
Select Report
      ↓
Press CONTINUE
      ↓
Uploading...
      ↓
Progress Indicator
      ↓
Upload Successful ✅
